Welcome to Red Sunset, an alternate history game based on Social Democracy by Autumn Chen (https://red-autumn.itch.io/social-democracy). This game attempts to be historically accurate, however, the choices taken by users playing through the game may result in outcomes that have not occurred in history, but could have theoretically happened, if different choices had been made.

The “Library” tab on the top left of the page will give you access to information about the Soviet Union, including Politburo members, political terms, and political/religious organizations. This section will provide essential background context, especially if you are unfamiliar with Red Sunset and Soviet Union history.

